         <div type="translation" xml:space="preserve"><head>Translation</head><p>Flavius Gaudentius, may you proceed in your good fortune; and in the name of Christ may the whole family of Severi live <note>omega and alpha on either side of a monogram cross</note>; farewell. This tower was built<supplied reason="undefined"> at a cost of</supplied><gap reason="lost" extent="unknown" unit="character"/> and 30 folles.</p></div>
